{"tid":1925640,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日有兩位手足死忌","createTime":"2020-03-14T13:52:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-15T06:13:27.000Z","uid":143774,"like":90,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"353346faea4f9e658769f3a3664836fc161703a3","tid":1925640,"uid":143774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T13:52:29.000Z","msg":"金鐘，梁淩杰手足<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0eLHaPL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0eLHaPL.jpg&h=86136260&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n浸大，熊家俊手足<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rOH2VgW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrOH2VgW.png&h=2c5d5cde&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k1SROCb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk1SROCb.png&h=407e1498&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有好多手足，死嘅死，殘嘅殘，可摸耳應承佢地，贏返個香港返嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n心淡/絕望嘅手足們，記得我地煲底之約，寧化飛灰，不作浮塵<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wHGWfjc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwHGWfjc.jpg&h=633ca116&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後死警死全家都唔夠，一撚定要睇住自己親人逐個逐個先死，最後自己百病纏身，係痛苦中死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4178a2fa18f38bd7ad5d4d6aabbe46568624302e","tid":1925640,"uid":89517,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T13:54:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e10913944096188633b5d558ae4fc6c86c8b1ab1","tid":1925640,"uid":39710,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T13:54:59.000Z","msg":"不忘記"},{"pid":"3d71b8e